POST-INSTALL:
	* Add the following line to your /usr/share/texmf/fonts/map/fontname/special.map file :
	ifsym           public          ikloeckl
	ifgeo           public          ikloeckl
	ifwea           public          ikloeckl
	ifclk           public          ikloeckl
	ifblk           public          ikloeckl


	* To take into account the ifsym class, you must execute 
	the command "texhash" as root:
	# texhash


